{"tid":2368718,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首階段美中貿易協定簽署一周年 中國未能兌現購買承諾","createTime":"2021-01-16T12:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T13:00:37.000Z","uid":75656,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd72fd989faacaf9001fd2f7ca0418afd5c8c70","tid":2368718,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:17:37.000Z","msg":"在購買美國商品方面，根據分析，截至11月，中國的實際購買量約為820億元，佔目標的大約52%。但相對地農產品上的表現，較製造業和能源商品更貼近目目標。皮特森國際經濟研究所（Peterson Institute for International Economics）資深院士鮑恩（Chad Bown）指出，中國在進口農產品上達到目標的67％、製造業商品52%、能源產品則只達31%。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國人口普查局的數據，即使中國未能達到購買目標，但美國對中國商品出口，與2019年的頭11個月同比增長了13%。與此同時，疫情引致的經濟活動減少令到中國商品進口下跌了5.8%。1至11月期間的美中雙邊貿易額下跌了12%，至2,830億元。<br />\n<br />\n對於北京有否履行承諾，中國海關總署新聞發言人李魁文引述數據表示，中國從美國進口的商品都有所增加，特別是大豆和豬肉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210116/ZISEVCKUPJAOLAG3RDDV6ZBWJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210116%2FZISEVCKUPJAOLAG3RDDV6ZBWJ4%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyPFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=5065dbad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210116%2FZISEVCKUPJAOLAG3RDDV6ZBWJ4%2F&h=85a21d3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210116/ZISEVCKUPJAOLAG3RDDV6ZBWJ4/</a>"},{"pid":"a0e3e40bc91f8e6d564a803295423b7adaec799b","tid":2368718,"uid":8308,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"歐盟班廢柴睇下啦"},{"pid":"1492e1236af978f87788f6b357fd69745975a4a1","tid":2368718,"uid":60853,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n這是常識吧<br />\n遵守到先唔正常"},{"pid":"5a999683c1442e53bb096b3aad5fe70a4cc5f2c0","tid":2368718,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:20:56.000Z","msg":"走數是常識吧"},{"pid":"e01282bb6ba2df3a865bb1d61cb0d6a9cf7e8066","tid":2368718,"u